g-the-loss-of-epic-160m-tv-opportunity.21352049 |arquivodata=29/5/2015 |último =Miller |primeiro =Phil |título=Beaten in Game of Thrones: why Scotland lost £160m chance to host TV series |url=http://www.heraldscotland.com/news/home-news/scotland-mourning-the-loss-of-epic-160m-tv-opportunity.21352049 |acessodata=17/6/2013 |jornal=[[The Herald]] |data=17/6/2013 |deadurl=no}}</ref>

